Docker to keep database isolated
 - docker-compose up

To create database schema and feed it
 - php -f database.php
 
To launch backend server
 - php -S 127.0.0.1:3100
 
To launch frontend server
 - npm i
 - npm start
 
 projet : 34h
 PHP 7.4
 mysql 8
 

